source, or

(2) Issuance of an enforcement policy statement to announce that the Commission will not apply the requirements of
the children's sleepwear standards to tight-fitting sleepwear garments and garments in infant sizes as long as those
garments meet the requirements of the clothing textiles flammability standard. 

Section 4(g) also requires the ANPR to include information about all standards known by the Commission to be relevant
